'''Gaston Pauls''' (b. [[January 17]], [[1972]] in [[Buenos Aires]]) is an [[Argentina|Argentine]] actor, TV host and producer.<ref>[http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0667282/ Gastón Pauls] at the [[Internet Movie Database]].</ref>

He started his career on television as a host of a [[videoclip]] show before starring in the teen [[soap opera]] "Montaña Rusa", where he met [[Nancy Duplaa]] who he dated for a few years. Pauls then starred on "Verdad Consecuencia" one of [[Adrian Suar]]'s first TV hits on [[Canal 13]]. 

As a stage actor he worked on "Desde la lona", "Porteños" and "La gata sobre el tejado de zinc caliente".

Pauls' first big movie role was in "Territorio comanche" alongside Cecilia Dopazo but his co-starring in [[Fabian Bielinsky]]'s "Nueve Reinas" brought him international acclaim.

He returned to television with "Tres padres solteros" and "Ser urbano" until 2006.

As of 2008, Pauls stars in [[comedy series]] "Todos contra Juan".

